products.title: Bella Primrose Roman Blind
products.description: This floral window blind is perfect for bringing a pretty touch plus practical shading to a kitchen or a bedroom. Using a cotton blend fabric with delicate embroidery in fresh yellow and green tones, the bella primrose roman blind is an uplifting option that is bursting with charm and will suit a traditionally inspired interior. Product id: db-rom1052 fabric colour: primrose material: 52% polyester 48% cotton lining: light filtering poly/cotton blended lining headrail: durable white headrail with top or face fix brackets.

products.title: Bella Primrose Curtain
products.description: The bella primrose curtain features a pretty floral motif that is enhanced with embroidery. This charming and delicate pattern is presented in a fresh springtime palette of green and yellow that will brighten up your interior any time of year. Fully lined, this curtain will provide excellent shading and will hang beautifully. Product id: db-cur1174 fabric colour: primrose material: 52% polyester 48% cotton lining: light filtering poly/cotton blended lining energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - increase to er3 (high) by adding thermal lining light filtering: yes bella primrose curtain in yellow/green.
